    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300179560_6_1046-1082",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1046-1082",
      "markText": "他浑身上下处处都很苍老，除了那双眼睛，它们跟海一个颜色，透着欢快与不屈。",
      "totalCount": 962,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300179560&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1046&rangeEnd=1082",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/46532e00813abaca4g010be6?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1046&rangeEnd=1082"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300179560_6_426-565",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "426-565",
      "markText": "他是个独自驾条小船在湾流打鱼的老人，现已出海八十四天，一条鱼也没捉到",
      "totalCount": 702,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300179560&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=426&rangeEnd=565",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/46532e00813abaca4g010be6?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=426&rangeEnd=565"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300179560_6_15686-15769",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "15686-15769",
      "markText": "他想，我把钓绳保持在精确的深度。只不过我不再走运了。可是谁说得准呢？也许今天行。每天都是个崭新日子。走运当然好。不过我宁愿搞得精确。这样，运气来临时，你就做好了准备。",
      "totalCount": 660,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300179560&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=15686&rangeEnd=15769",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/46532e00813abaca4g010be6?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=15686&rangeEnd=15769"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300179560_7_24183-24202",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "24183-24202",
      "markText": "不，你行的，他对自己说。你永远是行的。",
      "totalCount": 656,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300179560&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=24183&rangeEnd=24202",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/46532e00813abaca4g010be6?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=24183&rangeEnd=24202"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300179560_6_5069-5125",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5069-5125",
      "markText": "其实并没有渔网，孩子还记得是什么时候卖掉的。可是他们每天都要把这戏重演一遍。也没有鱼煮黄米饭，这一点孩子也知道。",
      "totalCount": 648,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300179560&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5069&rangeEnd=5125",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/46532e00813abaca4g010be6?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5069&rangeEnd=5125"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300179560_8_10014-10046",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "10014-10046",
      "markText": "现在不是想你没有什么东西的时候。想想你用现有的东西能做什么事吧。",
      "totalCount": 629,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300179560&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10014&rangeEnd=10046",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/46532e00813abaca4g010be6?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10014&rangeEnd=10046"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300179560_7_13283-13307",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "13283-13307",
      "markText": "他断定，只要他有强烈的取胜欲望，他就能击败任何人",
      "totalCount": 585,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300179560&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=13283&rangeEnd=13307",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/46532e00813abaca4g010be6?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=13283&rangeEnd=13307"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300179560_6_4316-4358",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "4316-4358",
      "markText": "再说老人虽然深信当地人不会来偷他的东西，但他觉得把鱼钩和鱼叉丢在船上总是不必要的诱惑",
      "totalCount": 561,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300179560&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4316&rangeEnd=4358",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/46532e00813abaca4g010be6?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=4316&rangeEnd=4358"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300179560_6_3282-3313",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3282-3313",
      "markText": "但他知道他已经变谦虚了，还知道这并不丢脸，也无损于真正的自尊。",
      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300179560&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3282&rangeEnd=3313",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/46532e00813abaca4g010be6?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3282&rangeEnd=3313"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300179560_7_4211-4253",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "4211-4253",
      "markText": "“好好休息一下，小鸟，”他说。“然后再去闯一闯，碰碰运气，像所有的人、鸟、鱼那样。”",
      "totalCount": 532,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300179560&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4211&rangeEnd=4253",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/46532e00813abaca4g010be6?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4211&rangeEnd=4253"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300179560_7_10262-10317",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "10262-10317",
      "markText": "他已经证实过上千次了，那都算不了什么。现在他要再证实一次。每一次都是一次新经历，他这么做的时候，从不去想过去。",
      "totalCount": 510,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300179560&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10262&rangeEnd=10317",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/46532e00813abaca4g010be6?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10262&rangeEnd=10317"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300179560_8_6414-6467",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6414-6467",
      "markText": "“想点开心事儿吧，老家伙，”他说。“每过一分钟，你就离家近一点。小船失去四十磅负重，行驶起来倒轻快些了。”",
      "totalCount": 500,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300179560&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6414&rangeEnd=6467",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/46532e00813abaca4g010be6?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6414&rangeEnd=6467"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300179560_8_6177-6198",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "6177-6198",
      "markText": "“顺着这条航线行驶吧，有了事情就担当着。”",
      "totalCount": 493,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300179560&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6177&rangeEnd=6198",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/46532e00813abaca4g010be6?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=6177&rangeEnd=6198"
    },
    {
